secrecy makes your spine to shiver. This is the command centre of Foun,
filled with computerized maps of numerous battlefields fought in different
times and worlds. The walls are surrounded by plate glass windows, with a
different view on each wall. The planes of Hell, Pandemonium, Tarterus and
Hades surround Foun's tower of Glass and Iron, giving him a view of his
realms. There are glass cabinets on the corners, with memorabilia from wars
long fought by Foun. Diffrent flags hang over them, from Roman legion Eagles
to SS Panzers. There are weapons from each era of war, starting from 16th
century flintlocks to M-16's. Uniforms of many diffrent armies are folded
neatly behind a long row of Armani suits.
