various stockmarkets and strengths of divisions. There are also few screens
running in Doom Deathmatch, abling Foun to play with his fellow Immortals.
Piles of books and magazines are piled on tables, all ranging from Playboy
to Sun Tsu's "the Art of War". The whole room seems to be in orderly chaos
like the world in itself.
